        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "Hearthstone AI was developed as part of my master's thesis and stands apart from the commercial work in the portfolio.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "The project focused on designing an AI agent for card-game decision making, using Monte Carlo Tree Search for evaluating game states.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "While it is not a frontend product case study, it adds useful depth to the portfolio by showing analytical thinking, systems reasoning, and long-form technical problem solving.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
